_sText:
This is a remake of a zombie panic source map called barrelhunters I believe. There are 3 t's vs 29 ct's. The cts are disguised in a box which blends in with the other boxes in the map and their only weapon is touching the T with the box to kill them. The T's get to find guns scattered across the map to fend off the ct boxes, but they are limited on ammo so It becomes a reverse cat n mouse game. Alota fun once it gets going.

Map made a while ago releasing now
Set for up to 32 spawns
